{"tid":1453940,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"想整合一個良心小店white list","createTime":"2019-08-12T05:45:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T04:09:31.000Z","uid":282718,"like":45,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"81f11d81e54b567ed0a726fba1ecc33e5b21aea3","tid":1453940,"uid":282718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:45:53.000Z","msg":"呢排成日見到罷食邊間 罷買邊間<br />\n好似我沉日出左個罷飲多間珍珠奶茶post<br />\n都有人提議不如整個white list<br />\n究竟邊啲商戶係可以 / 值得幫襯<br />\n入得呢個white list 既要有實質行動支持過今次呢個活動<br />\n派過物資 / 有罷過工 / proof 到佢係良心老闆 etc<br />\neven online shop 我覺得有實質行動支持過<br />\n都可以加入埋個list 到<br />\n<br />\n但我一個人無可能知道晒所有良心小店<br />\n所以我希望集合大家既力量 一齊報料<br />\n報料時 需要有店名 同埋 proof 到佢值得入white list 既野<br />\n我暫時應該會以excel形式整合<br />\n如果大家有其他意見 / 可以提供其他幫忙 歡迎提出<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a34f1b1bea2da46a6d16f25ed574b8b47ac8b82","tid":1453940,"uid":282718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:47:24.000Z","msg":"自推十次"},{"pid":"5ccde66f423e4e854040ca724f878d927c82e19f","tid":1453940,"uid":282718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:47:34.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"f03c23c9a72629e90f190d4eb3c33c371f70dd6a","tid":1453940,"uid":282718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:47:52.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"031785446393eb629f58886f6c44b8dcfc34f5e9","tid":1453940,"uid":282718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:48:02.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"43ac7643a8bb65505067231932b81463df728658","tid":1453940,"uid":282718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:48:15.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"6af42041a6d4d46bae30dcfb2ca413fb950e97b4","tid":1453940,"uid":282718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:48:30.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"6ff6b9b4b476293955b274d109bac618ba1df1c0","tid":1453940,"uid":282718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-